In order to install Solfec on CYGWIN:

1. From www.cygwin.com install CYGWIN.

2. Install additional packages:

   Devel/gcc
   Devel/make

   Python/python

   Math/lapack

   Libs/sunrpc
   Libs/libglut-devel
   Libs/libglut3

   X11/libGL-devel
   X11/libGL
   X11/libGLU-devel
   X11/libGLU
   X11/xorg-server
   X11/xinit
   X11/X-start-menu-icons
   X11/xterm

3. Start xterm from Cygwin/X menu (in Programs).

4. Change to a destination directory, e.g:
   cd /cygdrives/c/mydir

5. Place solfec.tar.gz in the destination directory.

6. Unpack it:
   tar -xzvf solfec.tar.gz

7. Go into solfec directory:
   cd solfec

8. Overwrite the configuration file:
   cp cfg/Config.CYGWIN ./Config.mak

9. Type:
   make clean
   make

10. Run some example files:
    ./solfec -v inp/arch.py
